hich was taken from the main symbol of the capital - the Eiffel Tower.\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 5025, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The peculiarity\", \"from\": 4908, \"to\": 4923}, {\"ngram\": \"these medals\", \"from\": 4927, \"to\": 4939}, {\"ngram\": \"the metal\", \"from\": 4943, \"to\": 4952}, {\"ngram\": \"the main symbol\", \"from\": 4975, \"to\": 4990}, {\"ngram\": \"the capital\", \"from\": 4994, \"to\": 5005}, {\"ngram\": \"the Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 5008, \"to\": 5024}]}, {\"sentence\": \"That is, the medals are an alloy of ordinary metal with gold, silver and bronze, respectively.\", \"from\": 5026, \"to\": 5120, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the medals\", \"from\": 5035, \"to\": 5045}, {\"ngram\": \"an alloy\", \"from\": 5050, \"to\": 5058}, {\"ngram\": \"ordinary metal\", \"from\": 5062, \"to\": 5076}, {\"ngram\": \"gold\", \"from\": 5082, \"to\": 5086}, {\"ngram\": \"silver\", \"from\": 5088, \"to\": 5094}, {\"ngram\": \"bronze\", \"from\": 5099, \"to\": 5105}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Remove the row Column: 1 Column: 2 Column: 3\", \"from\": 5122, \"to\": 5173, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the row\", \"from\": 5129, \"to\": 5136}, {\"ngram\": \"Column\", \"from\": 5137, \"to\": 5143}, {\"ngram\": \"1 Column\", \"from\": 5145, \"to\": 5153}, {\"ngram\": \"2 Column\", \"from\": 5155, \"to\": 5163}]}]}"